         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">[Melbourne,] ¶  17/9/61 ¶ Sir ¶  ¶ I am instructed by the Committee of the V. G. M. I. Society ¶  to convey to you their warmest thanks for your kindness in offering to place the Botanic Gardens at th...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">61.09.17</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Joseph Harris</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">MS 12521 Victorian Horticultural Society records, box 3401, p. 109, La Trobe Australian Manuscripts Collection, State Library of Victoria, Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">Trans. 28.9.94. To proof.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
               <note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">See also M to J. Harris, 19 September 1861.</p>
               </note>[Melbourne,]<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">editorial addition.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note> 17/9/61</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I am instructed by the Committee of the V. G. M. I. Society<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Victorian Gardeners' Mutual Improvement Society, Melbourne.</p>
               </note> to convey to you their warmest thanks for your kindness in offering to place the Botanic Gardens at their disposal for the purpose of holding an Exhibition, &amp; that they will avail themselves of the privilege in the last week of October —</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to remain Sir</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>yr. obedt Servt</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Joseph Harris (Hon: Sec:)</p>
         </div>
